  "title": "Class 3 Van Driver cum Pet Funeral Operations Specialist | Gross $3000+",
  "description": "<ul><li><p><strong>Role: Pet Funerals Operations Specialist cum Class 3 Driver</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Industry: Pet Funeral Services in Singapore</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>5.5 Days Role, random off day for 1.5 days</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>9am-5.30pm , 9am-1.30pm</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Salary range is $2,300 - $2500 Basic + $300 Allowance + OT</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Entitled to Twice Bonus Per Year</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Office location near Kaki Bukit / Ubi MRT</strong></p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ol><li><p>Valid Class 3 license and able to drive small auto van to perform job duties.</p></li><li><p>Able to work on public holidays and weekends, random off day.</p></li></ol><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><p><strong>Pet Transfers & Collection:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Handle the pickup and safe transportation of pets from homes, clinics, or hospitals with professionalism and empathy.</p></li><li><p>Ensure proper documentation, tagging, and chain-of-custody for every case.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Aquamation & Post-aquamation Processing:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Operate aquamation equipment following SOPs to ensure safety, quality, and dignity in every process.</p></li><li><p>Handle remains respectfully, drying of bones, preparing ashes and bone fragments for final placement</p></li></ul><p><strong>Pet Preparation</strong></p><ul><li><p>Grooming and cleaning of the pet</p></li></ul><p><strong>Memorial Room Preparation:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Set up the memorial room according to care specialist and family requests, including flowers, urns, lighting, and ceremonial arrangements.</p></li><li><p>Assist in facilitating private family farewells or rituals.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Aftercare & Ash Return:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Prepare ashes, keepsakes, and certificates for collection or delivery.</p></li><li><p>Conduct handovers and delivery with sensitivity and professionalism.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Facility Upkeep:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Maintain cleanliness and tidiness of work areas, equipment, and vehicles.</p></li><li><p>Conduct basic maintenance and ensure equipment readiness.</p></li><li><p>Conduct regular deep cleaning for crematorium equipment such as the water cremation machine</p></li></ul><p><strong>Team Collaboration:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Work in a team to support services, ceremonies, and daily operations.</p></li><li><p>Assist the care specialist to handle funeral arrangements</p></li><li><p>Uphold standards of empathy, detail, and excellence in every interaction.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Others</strong></p><ul><li><p>Ensuring proper records and documentation for each case handled</p></li><li><p>Assisting with operations admin such as printing tribute photos preparing pet food offerings</p></li><li><p>Any other adhoc tasks as required</p></li><li></li></ul><p>#SCR-carson-cheong</p><p>⭕ Cheong Kar Chun ⭕ Team Manager ⭕ R1980386</p><p>⭕ The Supreme HR Advisory ⭕ 14C7279</p><p><br />\n\n</p>",
